  "detailed_description": "Play as a member of the Cave Explorers. A team of specialist puzzle solvers who's role is to dodge traps and decipher clues in order to unlock hidden rooms and treasures for archaeologists to study.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437710/extras/7e493fa03421b94f112bd2239f55fb99.poster.avif?t=1633730703\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437710/extras/7e493fa03421b94f112bd2239f55fb99.webm?t=1633730703\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437710/extras/7e493fa03421b94f112bd2239f55fb99.mp4?t=1633730703\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Cave Explorers contains a wide variety of puzzles that will test your mechanical, intellectual and logic problem solving skills.<br>There are a number of unique zones to explore including: Desert, arctic, rainforest and a mystery zone.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1437710/extras/622745912b93848abab83928a473890e.avif?t=1633730703\" width=266 height=82 /></span>",
